  "prompt": "What are some cute names to call your boyfriend in Spanish?",
  "response": "Calling your boyfriend cute names in Spanish can be a sweet way to express affection. Here are some adorable and popular options:\n\n1. **Cari\u00f1o** \u2013 Darling / Sweetheart  \n2. **Amor** \u2013 Love  \n3. **Mi vida** \u2013 My life  \n4. **Coraz\u00f3n** \u2013 Heart  \n5. **Cielo** \u2013 Sky / Heaven  \n6. **Tesoro** \u2013 Treasure  \n7. **Churrito** \u2013 Little snack (playful and cute)  \n8. **Osito** \u2013 Little bear  \n9. **Mi rey** \u2013 My king  \n10. **Mi sol** \u2013 My sun  \n11. **Beb\u00e9** \u2013 Baby  \n12. **Media naranja** \u2013 My other half (literally \"half an orange\")  \n13. **Mi todo** \u2013 My everything  \n14. **Gatito** \u2013 Kitty (playful and sweet)  \n15. **Mi alma** \u2013 My soul  \n\nFeel free to mix and match these with possessive pronouns like **mi** (my) to make it even more personal, such as **mi cari\u00f1o** or **mi coraz\u00f3n**. \ud83d\ude0a",
